The paper proposes a novel approach for learning hierarchical and temporal representations using multiscale recurrent neural networks. This topic is relevant to several sub-categories in computer science, including machine learning (cs.LG), natural language processing (cs.CL), artificial intelligence (cs.AI), neural networks (cs.NE), and computer vision (cs.CV). Therefore, these are the most likely sub-categories for this paper.
